ABBYY Lingvo x3 is the new generation of electronic dictionaries. With 19 years of experience in the development of intelligent applications and lexicography work, ABBYY offers the ideal combination between language and software. This makes ABBYY Lingvo x3 the reliable language companion for both work and private everyday life.

ABBYY Lingvo x3 key features:

    * Authoritative and up-to-date language content
    * Reliable and accurate translations
    * Detailed entries with pronunciation keys and example sentences
    * Audio pronunciation of keywords recorded by native speakers
    * Easy and fast look-up
    * Flexible and expandable software
